VD Limitation for YOUR Project

Your app depends on:

Bluetooth (ESP32)
Real sensor data
Real-time streaming

👉 AVD does NOT support real BLE properly

🔥 Hybrid Testing Approach
1. Use AVD for:
UI screens
Graphs
Dashboard
Login system
2. Use REAL PHONE for:
BLE connection (ESP32)
Sensor data
Real-time alerts
Performance testing

👉 This is exactly how real companies build IoT apps.

Add a “Simulation Mode” toggle in your app:

ON → Use dummy/random sensor data (for AVD)
OFF → Use real BLE data (for phone)